FBIS4-11749 "drnes063_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 LEBANON Three Reportedly Killed in Amal Attack on Patrol Three Reportedly Killed in Amal Attack on Patrol NC3103170094 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 31 Mar 94 NC3103170094 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] The Amal Movement's operations room in the south has issued a statement saying that one of its units detonated an explosive device near an Israeli enemy and agent [South Lebanese Army] mechanized patrol on the Bra'shit-Bayt Yahun road at 1250 today. A half-track vehicle was completely destroyed and three personnel inside it were killed. Another unit attacked the same patrol with rockets and machine guns. The clash with the patrol lasted 15 minutes.
